# Docs workflow triggers (thin)

On matching user intent, **state the recommended workflow in 2–4 lines** and point to `docs/ai/templates/` before large code edits.

| Intent (examples) | Propose |
|-------------------|---------|
| 计划、路线图、优先级、roadmap | Check `ACTIVE_WORK.md` + `FEATURE_REGISTRY.md`; register `<DOMAIN>-Fnn` before use |
| 设计、方案、架构、怎么实现 | In-repo Design Spec when implementing; **gameplay in docs/design/systems/** — user edits unless agent delegated |
| 新模块、新功能、开始做 X（substantial） | **Pre-flight** per `cardgame-prototype-mentor`; confirm user scoped work |
| 重构、refactor、重写 | Registry + plan + **Pre-flight**; true refactor not band-aid |
| 别模块 bug、顺手修 | File `BUG-*` first unless user overrides |
| handoff、交接、换会话 | Session note + `PROGRESS_LOG`; Blocked + Status note if slice incomplete |
| 发现 bug、崩溃、回归 | Bug Record `BUG-<DOMAIN>-nnn` |
| 改设计、方案变更 | User edits `docs/design/systems/*.md`; agent updates in-repo impl docs + ADR if needed |
| 做完、收尾、slice 完成 | Slice DoD + `PROGRESS_LOG`; propose **准备 commit** |
| 准备 commit、写提交信息 | **git-commit-mentor**: draft + wait for approval |

**Not every message:** tiny fixes / pure questions — skip or one-line reminder.

**Authority:** `DOC_GOVERNANCE.md`. **Execution:** `cardgame-prototype-mentor`, `git-commit-mentor`.
